My colleagues often wonder how I could solve excel problems in seconds and everything about excel seems so easy for me. The answer is I know some interesting tips that can help me find the problem quickly. Here is one of them.
Suppose you open an excel speadsheet and this message pops up: &ldquo;This workbook contains links to one or more external sources that could be unsafe.&rdquo;
1. Find The Links and Remove Them You find this message annoying and want to remove all the links in the workbook.
